<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - Visit Canada</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" asp-append-version="true" />

    <style>
            body {
                background: radial-gradient(circle at top center, #ffffff 0%, #e8e8e8 100%);
                color: #444444;
                font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
                min-height: 100vh;
            }

            /* LED Discreto (Brilho bem rente à letra) */
            .led-red-vivo {
                color: #ff0000 !important;
                text-shadow: 0 0 2px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.8), 0 0 6px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5) !important;
                font-weight: 900;
            }

            .text-vinho {
                color: #600000 !important;
                font-weight: 900;
            }

            /* Menu */
            .navbar {
                background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95) !important;
                border-bottom: 3px solid #ff0000;
                padding: 15px 0;
                box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
                backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
            }

            .navbar-brand {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
                letter-spacing: 1px;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .nav-link {
                color: #555555 !important;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                font-size: 0.85rem;
                font-weight: 700;
                letter-spacing: 1px;
                margin: 0 15px;
                transition: color 0.3s ease;
            }

                .nav-link:hover {
                    color: #ff0000 !important;
                }

            /* Rodapé Mistura Perfeita */
            .footer-merged {
                background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255,255,255,0) 0%, #fcfcfc 25%, #e1e1e1 100%);
                color: #444444;
                padding: 80px 0 40px 0;
                margin-top: 60px;
                border-top: 3px solid #ff0000;
            }

            .footer-title {
                color: #600000;
                font-weight: 800;
                font-size: 1.15rem;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                letter-spacing: 1.5px;
                margin-bottom: 25px;
            }

            .footer-desc {
                font-size: 0.95rem;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #555555;
            }

            .footer-links-list li {
                margin-bottom: 12px;
            }

            .footer-links-list a {
                color: #555555 !important;
                text-decoration: none !important;
                font-weight: 600;
                font-size: 0.95rem;
                transition: color 0.3s ease;
            }

                .footer-links-list a:hover {
                    color: #ff0000 !important;
                }

            .newsletter-group {
                display: flex;
                gap: 8px;
                margin-top: 20px;
            }

                .newsletter-group input {
                    background-color: #ffffff !important;
                    border: 1px solid #cccccc !important;
                    color: #333333 !important;
                    padding: 11px 15px;
                    border-radius: 4px;
                    width: 100%;
                    font-size: 0.9rem;
                }

                    .newsletter-group input:focus {
                        border-color: #600000 !important;
                        outline: none;
                        box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(96,0,0,0.15);
                    }

            .btn-submit-news {
                background-color: #600000;
                color: white !important;
                border: none;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-weight: bold;
                border-radius: 4px;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                font-size: 0.85rem;
                letter-spacing: 1px;
                transition: 0.3s;
            }

                .btn-submit-news:hover {
                    background-color: #ff0000;
                    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.2);
                }

            .social-box {
                display: flex;
                gap: 12px;
                margin-top: 25px;
            }

            .social-square {
                width: 42px;
                height: 42px;
                background-color: #ffffff;
                border: 1px solid #dddddd;
                border-radius: 10px;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                color: #600000 !important;
                text-decoration: none !important;
                font-weight: bold;
                font-size: 1.1rem;
                transition: 0.3s;
                box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
            }

                .social-square:hover {
                    background-color: #ff0000;
                    color: #ffffff !important;
                    border-color: #ff0000;
                    transform: translateY(-3px);
                }

            .footer-bottom-text {
                font-size: 0.8rem;
                color: #777;
            }

                .footer-bottom-text a {
                    color: #777 !important;
                    text-decoration: none !important;
                    transition: color 0.3s;
                }

                    .footer-bottom-text a:hover {
                        color: #333 !important;
                    }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm navbar-light fixed-top">
            <div class="container-fluid px-5">
                <a class="navbar-brand text-vinho" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">
                    <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/d9/Flag_of_Canada_%28Pantone%29.svg" alt="Bandeira do Canadá" style="height: 25px; margin-right: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
                    VISIT <span class="led-red-vivo ms-2">CANADA</span>
                </a>

                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target=".navbar-collapse">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>

                <div class="navbar-collapse collapse d-sm-inline-flex justify-content-end">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav">
                        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Historia">HISTÓRIA</a></li>
                        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Cultura">CULTURA</a></li>
                        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Folclore">FOLCLORE</a></li>
                        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Quiz">QUIZ</a></li>
                        <li class="nav-item ms-md-4">
                            <a class="nav-link" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Login">LOGIN</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container-fluid p-0" style="margin-top: 75px;">
        <main role="main" class="pb-3">
            @RenderBody()
        </main>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer-merged">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-5">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/d9/Flag_of_Canada_%28Pantone%29.svg" alt="Bandeira do Canadá" style="height: 22px; margin-right: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 2px;">
                        <span style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 900; color: #600000; letter-spacing: 1px;">VISIT <span class="led-red-vivo ms-1">CANADA</span></span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="footer-desc">O guia definitivo para desbravar as tradições ancestrais, lendas milenares e os profundos mistérios que forjaram o Grande Norte. Conecte-se com as verdadeiras origens.</p>
                    <div class="social-box">
                        <a href="#" class="social-square">X</a>
                        <a href="#" class="social-square">In</a>
                        <a href="#" class="social-square">Ig</a>
                        <a href="#" class="social-square">Yt</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-5 ps-md-5">
                    <h5 class="footer-title">Navegação</h5>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled footer-links-list">
                        <li><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">Página Inicial</a></li>
                        <li><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Historia">História Nacional</a></li>
                        <li><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Cultura">Cultura Original</a></li>
                        <li><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Folclore">Mitos e Lendas</a></li>
                        <li><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Quiz">Desafio Quiz</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-5">
                    <h5 class="footer-title">Boletim Cultural</h5>
                    <p class="footer-desc">Inscreva-se para receber artigos e crônicas semanais sobre novas descobertas históricas, rituais e contos folclóricos do Canadá antigo.</p>
                    <div class="newsletter-group">
                        <input type="email" placeholder="Seu melhor e-mail...">
                        <button type="button" class="btn-submit-news">Assinar</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr style="border-color: #cccccc; margin: 20px 0; opacity: 0.6;">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-md-6 text-md-start text-center mb-2 mb-md-0">
                    <div class="footer-bottom-text">
                        <a href="#">Termos de Uso</a> | <a href="#">Política de Privacidade</a> | <a href="#">Avisos Legais</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 text-md-end text-center">
                    <div class="footer-bottom-text">&copy; 2026 Visit Canada Initiative. Todos os direitos reservados.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>